title: Although 2020 is not over yet, what 2020 song may possibly define the year? - Quora

response.answer_text: Take your pick:   My Corona:  “I’ve got chills, they’re multiplying”  “Hands, touching hands (NO!), touching me (DON’T DO IT!), touching you (AARGH NO, GET AWAY FROM ME!)  “I would walk 500 miles” Actually, you’re only allowed one hour’s exercise per day:  Don’t get this:  etc etc etc
Everything Is Awful by the Decembrists
